<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Landing Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../skydash-free/template/vendors/feather/feather.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../skydash-free/template/vendors/ti-icons/css/themify-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../skydash-free/template/vendors/css/vendor.bundle.base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../skydash-free/template/css/vertical-layout-light/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../skydash-free//template/images/favicon.png" />
    <style>
html, body {
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
}

.landing-page-container {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 0; 
}

.landing-content {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
}

.text-section {
    flex: 1;
}

.text-section h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0F8EC8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.nowrap-title {
    white-space: nowrap;
}

.text-section p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #6c757d;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.button-group a {
    min-width: 120px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border-radius: 30px;
    margin-right: 1rem;
}

.image-section {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 450px;
}

.image-section .large-logo {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

@media (max-width: 992px) {
    .landing-content {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .nowrap-title {
        white-space: normal;
    }
}


.btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #212529;
    text-align: center;
    vertical-align: middle;
    -webkit-user-select: none;
    -moz-user-select: none;
    -ms-user-select: none;
    user-select: none;
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    transition: color 0.15s ease-in-out, background-color 0.15s ease-in-out, border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out;
}

.btn:hover {
    color: #212529;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.btn:not(:disabled):not(.disabled) {
    cursor: pointer;
}

.btn-landingpage {
    background-color: #D7F2FF;
    background-image: none;
    border-color: #0F8EC8;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.btn-landingpage:not(.btn-inverse-light) {
    color: #0F8EC8;
}

.btn-landingpage:hover {
    background-color: #D7F2FF;
    color: #0F8EC8;
    border-color: #0F8EC8;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.btn-landingpage.focus, .btn-landingpage:focus {
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 142, 200, 0.5);
}

.btn-landingpage.disabled, .btn-landingpage:disabled {
    color: #0F8EC8;
    background-color: transparent;
}

.btn-landingpage.active, .btn-landingpage:active,
.show > .btn-landingpage.dropdown-toggle {
    color: #ffffff;
    background-color: #0F8EC8;
    border-color: #0F8EC8;
}
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container-scroller">
        <div class="landing-page-container">
            <main class="landing-content">
                <div class="text-section">
                    <h1>Satu Aplikasi untuk<br><span class="nowrap-title">Absensi & Laporan Harian</span></h1>
                    <p>Catat absensi dan kirim laporan harian langsung dari perangkat Anda, tepat waktu dan terintegrasi.</p>
                    <div class="button-group">
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-landingpage">Login</a>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-landingpage">Register</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="image-section">
                    <img src="../images/assets/1.png" alt="Foto Perpustakaan Medayu Agung" class="large-logo">
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
